QuestData.Title: Bleeding Hollow Supplies
QuestData.Description: The orcish ruins of Zeth'Gor to serve as a base for an ever-growing tide of orcs emerging from Hellfire Citadel.$B$BShadow Hunter Ty'jin sent me here to keep an eye on the outpost and its strange inhabitants.$B$BSomething has changed these orcs, augmented them in a way we've never seen before. We have to do anything we can to keep them from strengthening. Fight your way into Zeth'Gor and destroy any supplies you find there.
QuestData.LogDescription: Destroy 6 piles of Bleeding Hollow Supplies and report to Stone Guard Ambelan at Spinebreaker Post.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Return to Stone Guard Ambelan at Spinebreaker Post in Hellfire Peninsula.
